    .page {
      width: min(100%, 1180px);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 24px 16px 48px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .page::before,
    .page::after {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      z-index: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      border-radius: 999px;
      filter: blur(10px);
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    .page::before {
      width: 180px;
      height: 180px;
      top: -30px;
      left: -60px;
      background: rgba(255, 195, 165, 0.34);
    }

    .page::after {
      width: 220px;
      height: 220px;
      right: -80px;
      bottom: 50px;
      background: rgba(111, 194, 255, 0.18);
    }

    .hero {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .hero-note {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      background: #fff3d8;
      color: #8b542a;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(139, 84, 42, 0.12);
      transform: rotate(-2deg);
    }

    .hero h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      line-height: 1.35;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }

    .hero p {
      width: min(100%, 620px);
      margin: 12px auto 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--text-gray);
    }

    .control-bar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 4;
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      padding: 12px;
      margin: 0 auto 22px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.08);
    }

    .control-chip {
      appearance: none;
      border: 1px solid rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.08);
      background: var(--white);
      color: var(--text-black);
      border-radius: var(--radius-chip);
      min-height: 43px;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, background 0.25s ease, color 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
    }

    .control-chip.is-active {
      background: var(--dark-blue);
      color: var(--white);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.24);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .overview {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      margin-bottom: 26px;
    }

    .overview-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);
      border: 1px solid rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.08);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    }

    .overview-card span {
      display: block;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .overview-card strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 22px;
      line-height: 1.3;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .screens {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: grid;
      gap: 24px;
      justify-items: center;
    }

    .screen {
      width: 100%;
      display: none;
      align-items: start;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 18px;
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(12px);
      transition: opacity 0.35s ease, transform 0.35s ease;
    }

    .screen.is-active {
      display: flex;
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    .screen-copy {
      width: min(100%, 360px);
      padding-top: 24px;
    }

    .screen-copy .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      gap: 8px;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      background: #fff1e8;
      color: #b2544f;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      transform: rotate(-2deg);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .screen-copy h2 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 28px;
      line-height: 1.35;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .screen-copy p {
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.85;
      color: var(--text-gray);
    }

    .screen-copy ul {
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
      list-style: none;
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .screen-copy li {
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.08);
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-black);
    }

    .phone-shell {
      position: relative;
      width: min(100%, var(--screen-width));
      min-height: var(--screen-height);
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 38px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #243279 0%, #10173f 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(9, 19, 85, 0.32);
    }

    .phone-shell::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: 10px;
      left: 50%;
      width: 136px;
      height: 24px;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      background: #0f1330;
      border-radius: 0 0 18px 18px;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .phone-body {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      min-height: calc(var(--screen-height) - 24px);
      border-radius: 30px;
      background: var(--gradient-warm);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.24);
    }

    .screen-bg-shape,
    .screen-bg-shape2,
    .screen-bg-doodle {
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 999px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .screen-bg-shape {
      width: 210px;
      height: 210px;
      top: -60px;
      right: -40px;
      background: rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.16);
    }

    .screen-bg-shape2 {
      width: 180px;
      height: 180px;
      left: -80px;
      bottom: 80px;
      background: rgba(29, 220, 255, 0.12);
    }

    .screen-bg-doodle {
      width: 94px;
      height: 94px;
      right: 10px;
      bottom: 110px;
      border: 2px dashed rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.26);
      transform: rotate(14deg);
    }

    .status-row {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: calc(var(--safe-top) + 6px) 18px 10px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .app-frame {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      padding: 6px 18px 26px;
    }

    .badge-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .mini-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      padding: 7px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.08);
    }

    .headline-card {
      position: relative;
      padding: 18px 18px 20px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .headline-card::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: auto -18px -18px auto;
      width: 86px;
      height: 86px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.12);
    }

    .label-hand {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #fff1e2;
      color: #b55b33;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      transform: rotate(-4deg);
    }

    .headline-card h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 30px;
      line-height: 1.35;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .headline-card p {
      margin: 8px 0 0;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--text-gray);
    }

    .car-card {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 84px 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-card);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .car-illustration {
      position: relative;
      width: 84px;
      height: 84px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f6f8ff 0%, #d7eaff 100%);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .car-illustration::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 14px;
      bottom: 28px;
      width: 56px;
      height: 22px;
      border-radius: 18px 18px 10px 10px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff8bb4, #f84ca2);
    }

    .car-illustration::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 22px;
      bottom: 42px;
      width: 34px;
      height: 14px;
      border-radius: 12px 12px 4px 4px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.84);
    }

    .wheel {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 20px;
      width: 12px;
      height: 12px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .wheel.left {
      left: 20px;
    }

    .wheel.right {
      right: 16px;
    }

    .car-meta h4 {
      margin: 2px 0 6px;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .car-meta p {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--text-gray);
    }

    .price-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: end;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .price-row strong {
      font-family: "Righteous", "Noto Sans JP", sans-serif;
      font-size: 30px;
      line-height: 1;
      color: var(--pink);
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .price-row span {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      padding-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .prediction-card,
    .expense-card,
    .compare-card,
    .support-card {
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .section-title {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .section-title strong {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .section-title span {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
    }

    .segmented {
      display: inline-flex;
      gap: 6px;
      padding: 4px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #f1f4ff;
    }

    .segment-btn {
      appearance: none;
      border: 0;
      min-width: 64px;
      min-height: 34px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.25s ease, color 0.25s ease;
    }

    .segment-btn.is-active {
      background: var(--dark-blue);
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .chart {
      position: relative;
      height: 166px;
      padding: 12px 0 0;
    }

    .chart-grid {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 12px 0 22px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-rows: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }

    .chart-grid span {
      border-top: 1px dashed rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.12);
    }

    .chart-svg {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
    }

    .chart-points {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: end;
      position: absolute;
      inset: 24px 0 36px;
      padding: 0 10px;
    }

    .chart-node {
      width: 14px;
      height: 14px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--pink);
      border: 4px solid rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.16);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.06);
    }

    .chart-labels {
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
    }

    .forecast-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 8px;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    .forecast-tile {
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: #f7f8ff;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .forecast-tile span {
      display: block;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .forecast-tile strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .support-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 241, 226, 0.98), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98));
      border: 1px solid rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.12);
    }

    .support-card p {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: #7b5a4d;
    }

    .action-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn-primary,
    .btn-secondary {
      appearance: none;
      border: 0;
      min-height: 43px;
      padding: 0 18px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-button);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease, opacity 0.25s ease;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--gradient-primary);
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(77, 180, 255, 0.34);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: var(--gradient-pink);
      color: var(--white);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.22);
    }

    .btn-primary:active,
    .btn-secondary:active,
    .control-chip:active,
    .segment-btn:active {
      transform: scale(0.98);
    }

    .expense-summary {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .summary-tile {
      padding: 12px 10px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: #f8fbff;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .summary-tile span {
      display: block;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .summary-tile strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .bars {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .bar-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 68px 1fr 48px;
      gap: 8px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .bar-row label {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .bar-track {
      position: relative;
      height: 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #eff2fb;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .bar-fill {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0 auto 0 0;
      width: 0;
      border-radius: inherit;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffc6d6, #f84ca2);
      transition: width 0.6s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1);
    }

    .bar-row strong {
      text-align: right;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .insight-banner {
      margin-top: 12px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(29, 220, 255, 0.12), rgba(77, 180, 255, 0.18));
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .compare-toggle {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .compare-pill {
      appearance: none;
      border: 1px solid rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.08);
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      border-radius: 999px;
      min-height: 38px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .compare-pill.is-active {
      background: var(--dark-blue);
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .compare-table {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .compare-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 8px;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: #f8f9ff;
    }

    .compare-row.header {
      background: transparent;
      padding: 0 4px 4px;
    }

    .compare-row span {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-weight: 700;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .compare-row span:first-child {
      text-align: left;
    }

    .compare-row strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .compare-row strong.good {
      color: #0d7c6d;
    }

    .compare-row strong.warn {
      color: #ba5a24;
    }

    .callout-zero {
      margin: 14px 0 10px;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff0f5, #fff8ed);
      border: 1px solid rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.14);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .callout-zero span {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #b25d4a;
    }

    .callout-zero strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 36px;
      line-height: 1;
      color: var(--pink);
      font-family: "Righteous", "Noto Sans JP", sans-serif;
    }

    .callout-zero p {
      margin: 8px 0 0;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--text-gray);
    }

    .footer-note {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      margin-top: 26px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--text-gray);
    }

    .pulse {
      animation: pulse 1.8s infinite;
    }

    .floaty {
      animation: floaty 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .draw-line {
      stroke-dasharray: 600;
      stroke-dashoffset: 600;
      animation: drawLine 1.4s ease forwards;
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
      45% { transform: scale(1.03); }
    }

    @keyframes floaty {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(-2deg); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-5px) rotate(-3deg); }
    }

    @keyframes drawLine {
      to { stroke-dashoffset: 0; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 979px) {
      .overview {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .screen {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .screen-copy {
        width: min(100%, var(--screen-width));
        padding-top: 0;
      }

      .screen-copy h2 {
        font-size: 24px;
      }
    }

    @media (min-width: 980px) {
      .screen {
        width: 100%;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 420px) {
      .page {
        padding-left: 10px;
        padding-right: 10px;
      }

      .hero h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
      }

      .phone-shell {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .headline-card h3 {
        font-size: 27px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-note">ストアPV→DL率改善を想定した感情訴求スクショ案</div>
      <h1>不安をほどいて、<br>「今の価値」と「これから」を一目で伝える</h1>
      <p>
        AI査定の安心感、出費の見える化、そして相場チェック時点では電話0本。
        初めて売却を考える人の迷いを、やさしく減らすストアスクリーンの試作です。
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="control-bar" aria-label="スクリーン切り替え">
      <button class="control-chip is-active" data-target="screen-a">スクショA / iOS</button>
      <button class="control-chip" data-target="screen-b">スクショB / Android</button>
      <button class="control-chip" data-target="screen-c">スクショC / 比較</button>
    </div>

    <section class="overview">
      <article class="overview-card">
        <span>主訴求</span>
        <strong>AIが愛車の今をやさしく査定</strong>
      </article>
      <article class="overview-card">
        <span>感情価値</span>
        <strong>売るか迷う段階でも不安を増やさない</strong>
      </article>
      <article class="overview-card">
        <span>差別化</span>
        <strong>個人情報なしで相場チェック、将来予測つき</strong>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="screens">
      <article class="screen is-active" id="screen-a">
        <div class="screen-copy">
          <div class="eyebrow">iOS向け / AI査定を全面訴求</div>
          <h2>「この車、いくら？」を<br>安心して始められる1枚</h2>
          <p>
            ピンクの査定額を主役にしながら、個人情報不要の安心感と将来予測を同時に提示。
            最初の一歩に必要な情報だけを、やわらかく整理しています。
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>愛車の具体例: 2019年式 トヨタ プリウス S / 72,400km</li>
